            <div class="text-primary dark:text-primary-dark">â˜…â˜…â˜…â˜…â˜…</div>
          </div>
          <p class="text-text-secondary-light dark:text-text-secondary-dark mb-4">"cramti.me helped me score a 5 on my AP Calculus exam. The practice problems were exactly what I needed!"</p>
