          <div class="font-medium dark:text-white">Shlok S., SAT Student</div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="bg-surface-light dark:bg-surface-secondary-dark p-5 md:p-6 rounded-lg shadow-sm">
          <div class="flex items-center mb-4">
            <div class="text-primary dark:text-primary-dark">â˜…â˜…â˜…â˜…â˜…</div>
          </div>
          <p class="text-text-secondary-light dark:text-text-secondary-dark mb-4">"I improved my SAT score by 200 points after using cramti.me for just two months. Highly recommend!"</p>
